channel.description: I use a client and source called "Rune LookaLike." Prayers don't work, and for some reason, I connect just by hitting runserver and opening up the client, (before I switch all the java shit, (compiler etc.)) and if I .rar my client and upload it and send the link to someone, they don't connect. I need help, thanks.
